data.description: What a view of Lake Superior from high above Crow Creek! New-and-improved 4BR/3BA rambler with 2-car attached garage on 7.11 acres. Updated kitchen with new tile floor and beautiful butcher block center island with seating. The sun shines bright on the main floor with huge windows facing the lake and gleaming hard wood floors. Three main floor bedrooms, one with attached new 3/4 bath and main floor laundry. The spacious basement with huge rec room and additional kitchen could provide great potential for a mother-in-law apartment or short/long term rental (verified with Lake County that this property does meet the specifications for a short term or long term rental!). The inviting basement space also boasts a sauna and a gas fireplace. Compliant septic.  Electric: $93.50/mo average Propane: 1,370 gallons delivered last year
